65
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,160
Ye Peminat!

66
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:56,520
Lawan kau adalah aku!

67
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,000
Taiyin Shenzi (Anak Bulan)

68
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:02,520
Awak masih hidup?

69
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,640
Kau memegang Matahari,

70
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,960
Aku berasal dari Taiyin (Bulan).

71
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,840
Semua benda yang wujud mempunyai kaunter semula jadi mereka.

72
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,360
Kitab Suci Sejati Matahari dalam dirimu

73
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,640
