95
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:49,080
Pembuangan Abadi!

96
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,240
Tolak!

97
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,200
Bunuh!

98
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,400
Tengkorak saya!

99
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,040
Tidak!

100
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,640
Ini milik saya!

101
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,600
Pak Cik Jiang!

102
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,720
Aku tak nak kau mati!

103
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,520
Pak Cik Jiang...

104
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,680
Aku takkan dapat tengok kau membesar.

105
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:36,840
Pelayan tua ini tidak cekap.

106
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,360
Malu di hadapan Maharaja Suci!

107
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,600
Oleh kerana aku telah menerima rahmat Maharaja Santo Matahari,

108
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,800
selagi aku hidup,

109
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,520
Aku sama sekali tidak akan membiarkan dia terluka.

110
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,880
Terima kasih...

111
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,880
Awak mesti...

112
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,040
melindunginya.

113
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,040
Pak Cik Jiang!

114
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,440
Pak Cik Jiang!

115
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:04,800
Pak Cik Jiang!

116
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,920
Jangan pergi!

117
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,600
Saya tiada keluarga lagi.

118
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:09,960
Pak Cik Jiang...

119
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,280
Pak Cik Jiang...

120
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,000
Ayah, Ibu...

121
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,560
Adik-beradik...

122
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,960
Tiada seorang pun antara kamu di sini lagi.

123
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,360
Tupai Kecil...

124
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,640
Adakah anda merindui keluarga anda?

125
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:30,400
Tongtong...

126
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,280
Pak Cik Jiang dan keluarga awak...

127
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,800
