159
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:38,560
Ini...

160
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,720
Guru...

161
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,360
Setiap malam ketika aku tidur,

162
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:47,760
