166
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,600
Warisan Maharaja Santo Umat Manusia belum terputus.

167
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,200
Tongtong...

168
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,360
Guru...

169
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:05,800
Sekarang...

170
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,200
anda telah mendapat sedikit asas.

171
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,720
Aku mesti terus mencari jalan pulang.

172
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,800
Jom pergi.

173
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,160
Tuan Muda...

174
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,400
Kapal Perang Tembaga Ungu telah terhalang di Bintang Ziwei.

175
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:20,760
Dihalang oleh Manusia Suci yang tiba-tiba muncul, Putera Tianxuan.

176
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,880
Walau bagaimanapun, dia bukanlah tandingan bagi Santo Agung Seribu Tangan itu.

177
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,800
Dia sepatutnya sudah mati dalam pertempuran sekarang.

178
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,760
Tetapi Tubuh Suci yang berdekatan mencetuskan hantu dan aura Syaitan Manusia.

179
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,440
Puak itu agak panik.

180
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,120
Kita tunggu keputusan Tuan Muda.

181
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,320
Baguslah orang tua gila itu sudah mati.

182
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,200
Jika tidak, dia benar-benar akan menyusahkan.

183
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,680
Bagi syaitan tua Dongfang Taiyi itu...

184
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,000
dia sendiri yang bermasalah.

185
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,600
Tak perlu pedulikan dia langsung.

186
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:49,440
Namun, Ye Fan ini benar-benar pelik.

187
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,560
Insiden Tubuh Suci dalam Keluarga Ji merupakan satu pembolehubah.

188
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,040
Saya tidak suka.

189
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,600
Difahamkan.

190
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:56,800
Kami...

191
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:59,640
akan mengurangkan semua perkara yang berkaitan dengan pembolehubah ini.

192
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,320
Bangsa Manusia...

193
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:06,720
Anak Ilahi akan dilahirkan.

194
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,000
Raja-Raja Leluhur akan kembali.

195
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,920
Menjelang masa itu, kita akan memimpin Big Dipper bersama-sama.

196
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:12,840
Keturunan Maharaja Syurgawi...

197
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,400
