208
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,160
Ye Fan...

209
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,040
Ziyue...

210
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:04,920
Guru...

211
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,600
Awak sebenarnya mimpi ngeri ke?

212
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,720
Saya bermimpi melihat Bintang Biduk...

213
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,560
ditewaskan oleh tentera Bangsa Purba.

214
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,600
Kawan-kawan saya bergelut sambil bermandikan darah.

215
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:16,920
Saya mahu balik!

216
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,040
Guru...

217
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,440
Kuasa tertinggi tahap anda...

218
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:20,760
jarang sekali menghasilkan mimpi seperti ini.

219
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,560
Bolehkah ia menjadi mimpi nubuatan, satu tanda?

220
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:30,960
Guru...

221
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:31,800
Mungkin...

222
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,240
hanya hati yang dipenuhi dengan kebimbangan dan keresahan.

223
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,280
Di mana hati berada...

224
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:37,080
